name: Giant Scorpion Worm
description: The Giant Mutant Worms have evolved and taken over a hostile alien planet. Some now have legs, and even stingers! Although these creatures have legs, their bodies lack an exoskeleton. Other than the stinger and limbs, the body is soft and slimy. Beware the world is very dangerous! These worms have veracious appetites, and have been known to toss people high into the air as they devour them! These species can be viewed in VR on AltspaceVr under Giant Mutand Worms, Evolution Giant Mutant worms 2021. World Code AOI074. Micah J @vr_micahj  ig:MicahJ_VR
